      "title": "I.O.C. Reduces fuel prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian Oil Company (I.O.C.) also took steps to lower fuel prices today (17) afternoon.",
        "According to the IOC, a liter of Octane 92 petrol will be sold at 450 rupees, a liter of Octane 95 petrol at 540 rupees, a liter of auto diesel at 440 rupees and a liter of super diesel at 510 rupees from 10.00 tonight. says."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "I.O.C. Reduces",
